<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderPassNode.RemoveChildNodes" Title="RemoveChildNodes method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderPassNode">IRenderPassNode</PageRef> ->
    RemoveChildNodes
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>RemoveChildNodes</TypeRef> method removes the specified set of <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IProgramNode">IProgramNode</PageRef>
      objects from the list of child nodes if present.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void RemoveChildNodes(IProgramNode* const* childNodes, size_t childNodeCount);
void RemoveChildNodes(IProgramNode::unique_ptr const* childNodes, size_t childNodeCount);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="IProgramNode* const* / IProgramNode::unique_ptr const*!cobalt.graphics.IProgramNode" Name="childNodes">
          The set of <TypeRef>IProgramNode</TypeRef> objects to remove from the list of child nodes
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="size_t" Name="childNodeCount">
          The number of <TypeRef>IProgramNode</TypeRef> entries to read from the <TypeRef>childNodes</TypeRef> array
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
